span><span><br></span><span>특히 감기나 중이염 때문에 코나 귀에 비내시경를 넣고 <br></span><span>검사를 해야하는데 <br></span><span>무서워하는 아이들이 많습니다<br></span><span><br></span><span><br></span><span>그럴때 아이들에게 이 뽀로로 비타민을 <br></span><span>주면 아이들이 뚝 하고 이 비타민을 좋아하지 <br></span><span>않을까요? ㅎㅎㅎ</span><span></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1523436889092-1522088520_image_1_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6d4970ec7438d751.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1523436889092-1522088520_image_1_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6d4970ec7438d751.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6d4970ec7438d751.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"960\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" data-attachment-id=\"IDhvCjL3WjOYq0C0qNDk4eYteD6s\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>품질보증검사필 스티커도 있어요<br></span><span><br